data.description: Pride of ownership in this 1854 farmhouse meticulously maintained and decorator perfect. High ceilings and detail of yesteryear blend blend with modern floor plan of large kitchen with sitting area and dining space plus mudroom and office area. Large Family room with gas fireplace. Third floor suite has bath and built ins and skylight Formal dining room will take your breath away. Private rear yard with deck. This is a truly extraordinary home
